    Status enum for `ActionRun.cs`: use the ADR-017 canonical 6 values exactly: `Queued`, `Running`, `Completed`, `Failed`, `Poisoned`, `Cancelled`. Add `[JsonStringEnumConverter]` for clean serialization.

    `ActionDefinition.cs` model fields mirror `sprk_action` from task 010. Property naming uses camelCase via `[JsonPropertyName]` if the Dataverse fields are PascalCase-stored â€” verify against task 010's schema doc.
